準。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/HT208191\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fzh-hk%2FHT208191&d=wPrWLGb7qtEQEAFsbU3d2o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=abb1b568\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/HT208191</a><br />\n<br />\nApple 自己都戴定頭盔免責<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7487b6011faee2e35161e89c6acbb3af1f87dbe","tid":459842,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:25:12.000Z","msg":"連登真係 <br />\n將led 缺點無限放大"},{"pid":"f749499353ab0e954158109f2aded9d8be8fc567","tid":459842,"uid":19557,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:26:11.000Z","msg":"根本完全係一部測試機黎 如果比SJ 見到今日咁 真係激到佢彈返起身 <br />\n當年SJ要做部機最完美先可以比佢推出市場 就算有小小問題佢都唔會比佢加落部新機度<br />\n今日gay cook 真係搞壞曬apple 聲譽"},{"pid":"77b8ce8349d2698cd77ef3b6f897ff3f3f196129","tid":459842,"uid":45242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:10:29.000Z","msg":"有問題可以免費換mon ，"},{"pid":"e4391a2cf494e391d31a6f2f307bd150598026f8","tid":459842,"uid":51717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T03:03:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登真係 <br />\n將led 缺點無限放大</blockquote><br />\nidoge更厲害<br />\n將iPhone缺點無限縮少，甚至話係無缺點，人哋講都唔得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d671461d1517fa6e6124048e223bb03efe163af9","tid":459842,"uid":51269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T03:19:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連登真係 <br />\n將led 缺點無限放大</blockquote><br />\nidoge更厲害<br />\n將iPhone缺點無限縮少，甚至話係無缺點，人哋講都唔得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當年烙印戰士個名就係ifan講先，拎黎笑三星啲amoled，以前都話左啲i狗龍門任搬架啦。<br />\n<br />\n同埋係oled同led兩回事黎，個技術唔同的"},{"pid":"a7721e6f019895b470b30ab225870bebf1daaeaa","tid":459842,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score